item.title: Exercise PIÈCES MOBILES / Exercice Pièces Mobiles
item.description:
Exercise PIÈCES MOBILES / Exercice Pièces Mobiles

Approximately 150 soldiers from 5e Régiment d'artillerie légère du Canada (5 RALC) take part in exercise PIÈCE MOBILE, March 21-23, 2016. The training objective is to validate and maintain the skills of artillerymen, who are in a state of high operational readiness.
